info.author: daizutabi
info.description: Pheasant is a Markdown converter which is designed to be used as a plugin for static site generators, especially MkDocs. The Pheasant main feature is auto generation of outputs for a fenced code block in Markdown source using Jupyter client. In addition, Pheasant can automatically number headers, figures, tables, etc.
